class="code-block_container__lbMX4"><pre class="m-0 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-none px-4 py-3 font-mono text-[#24292e] dark:text-[#e1e4e8]"><code class="text-[11px] leading-normal sm:text-[13px]">import streamlit as st
import pandas as pd
import qrcode
from PIL import Image
from reportlab.pdfgen import canvas
from reportlab.lib.pagesizes import A4
from reportlab.lib.utils import ImageReader
import io
import os
import zipfile

# ====================== KONFIGURASI HALAMAN ======================
st.set_page_config(
page_title=&quot;Tamima E-Voucher Generator&quot;,
page_icon=&quot;&quot;,
layout=&quot;wide&quot;
)

# ====================== CSS KUSTOM ======================
st.markdown(&quot;&quot;&quot;
&lt;style&gt;
.stButton&gt;button {

}

}
&lt;/style&gt;
&quot;&quot;&quot;, unsafe_allow_html=True)

# ====================== HEADER ======================
st.title(&quot; **Tamima E-Voucher Generator**&quot;)
st.markdown(&quot;*Aplikasi Generate Voucher PDF dengan QR Code &amp; Logo*&quot;)

# ====================== SIDEBAR: PENGATURAN LOGO ======================
st.sidebar.header(&quot; Pengaturan&quot;)

logo_option = st.sidebar.radio(
&quot;Pilih Sumber Logo:&quot;,
[&quot;Default (logo_tamima.png)&quot;, &quot;Upload Custom&quot;],
key=&quot;logo_source&quot;
)

logo_image = None

if logo_option == &quot;Upload Custom&quot;:
logo_file = st.sidebar.file_uploader(
&quot;Upload Logo (PNG/JPG)&quot;,
type=[&quot;png&quot;, &quot;jpg&quot;, &quot;jpeg&quot;],
key=&quot;logo_upload&quot;
)
if logo_file:
try:
logo_image = Image.open(logo_file)
st.sidebar.success(&quot; Logo berhasil dimuat&quot;)
except Exception as e:
st.sidebar.error(f&quot; Gagal memuat logo: {e}&quot;)
else:
st.sidebar.info(&quot; Silakan upload file logo&quot;)
else:
# Coba load logo default
try:
if os.path.exists(&quot;logo_tamima.png&quot;):
logo_image = Image.open(&quot;logo_tamima.png&quot;)
st.sidebar.success(&quot; Logo default ditemukan&quot;)
else:
st.sidebar.warning(&quot; File &#x27;logo_tamima.png&#x27; tidak ditemukan di folder proyek&quot;)
st.sidebar.info(&quot;Silakan upload logo manual atau letakkan file logo_tamima.png di folder yang sama dengan app.py&quot;)
except Exception as e:
st.sidebar.error(f&quot; Error memuat logo: {e}&quot;)

# ====================== FUNGSI UTILITY ======================
def generate_qr_bytes(data):
&quot;&quot;&quot;
Generate QR Code dan return sebagai BytesIO.
Tidak menyimpan file permanen ke disk.
&quot;&quot;&quot;
try:
qr = qrcode.QRCode(
version=1,
error_correction=qrcode.constants.ERROR_CORRECT_L,
box_size=10,
border=2
)
qr.add_data(data)
qr.make(fit=True)
img = qr.make_image(fill_color=&quot;black&quot;, back_color=&quot;white&quot;)
buffer = io.BytesIO()
img.save(buffer, format=&#x27;PNG&#x27;)
buffer.seek(0)
return buffer
except Exception as e:
st.error(f&quot;Error generating QR: {e}&quot;)
raise

def create_pdf_voucher(row, logo_img):
&quot;&quot;&quot;
Membuat PDF voucher untuk satu baris data.
Menggunakan ReportLab dengan ukuran A4.
&quot;&quot;&quot;
buffer = io.BytesIO()
c = canvas.Canvas(buffer, pagesize=A4)
width, height = A4
try:
# === HEADER: LOGO &amp; JUDUL ===
if logo_img:
logo_reader = ImageReader(logo_img)
# Logo di kiri atas (x=50, y dari atas -100)
c.drawImage(
logo_reader,
x=50,
y=height - 100,
width=100,
height=80,
preserveAspectRatio=True,
anchor=&#x27;c&#x27;
)
# Judul
c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica-Bold&quot;, 20)
c.drawString(160, height - 70, &quot;E-VOUCHER TAMIMA&quot;)
# Subjudul
c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica&quot;, 12)
c.drawString(160, height - 90, &quot;Hajj &amp; Umrah Service&quot;)
# Garis pemisah warna emas (RGB: 0.8, 0.6, 0.2)
c.setStrokeColorRGB(0.8, 0.6, 0.2)
c.setLineWidth(3)
c.line(50, height - 110, width - 50, height - 110)
# === BODY: DETAIL VOUCHER ===
c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica-Bold&quot;, 12)
start_y = height - 150
line_height = 30
label_x = 60
value_x = 180
# Data yang akan ditampilkan (pastikan semua string)
details = [
(&quot;Order ID&quot;, str(row[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;])),
(&quot;Nama Tamu&quot;, str(row[&#x27;Nama_Tamu&#x27;])),
(&quot;Properti&quot;, str(row[&#x27;Properti&#x27;])),
(&quot;Layanan&quot;, str(row[&#x27;Layanan&#x27;])),
(&quot;Check-in&quot;, str(row[&#x27;Check_in&#x27;])),
(&quot;Check-out&quot;, str(row[&#x27;Check_out&#x27;])),
(&quot;Status&quot;, str(row[&#x27;Status&#x27;]))
]
for i, (label, value) in enumerate(details):
y_pos = start_y - (i * line_height)
# Label bold
c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica-Bold&quot;, 11)
c.drawString(label_x, y_pos, f&quot;{label} :&quot;)
# Value normal
c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica&quot;, 11)
c.drawString(value_x, y_pos, value)
# === QR CODE ===
qr_content = f&quot;OrderID:{row[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;]}|Guest:{row[&#x27;Nama_Tamu&#x27;]}|Status:{row[&#x27;Status&#x27;]}&quot;
qr_buffer = generate_qr_bytes(qr_content)
# ReportLab butuh path file untuk drawImage, jadi buat temp file sementara
temp_qr_path = f&quot;temp_qr_{row[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;]}_{hash(str(row[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;]))}.png&quot;
try:
# Simpan ke temp file
with open(temp_qr_path, &quot;wb&quot;) as f:
f.write(qr_buffer.getvalue())
# Gambar QR di kanan (posisi x=width-200, y=tinggi dari atas -250)
c.drawImage(temp_qr_path, width - 200, height - 250, width=120, height=120)
# Label QR Code
c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica&quot;, 9)
c.drawString(width - 195, height - 265, &quot;Scan untuk verifikasi&quot;)
finally:
# Pastikan temp file selalu dihapus meski error
if os.path.exists(temp_qr_path):
os.remove(temp_qr_path)
# === FOOTER ===
footer_y = 80
c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica-Oblique&quot;, 9)
c.setFillColorRGB(0.3, 0.3, 0.3)
c.drawString(60, footer_y, &quot;Syarat &amp; Ketentuan:&quot;)
c.drawString(60, footer_y - 15, &quot; Voucher berlaku 6 (enam) bulan sejak tanggal pembelian.&quot;)
c.drawString(60, footer_y - 30, &quot; Tidak dapat digabungkan dengan promo atau diskon lainnya.&quot;)
c.drawString(60, footer_y - 45, &quot; Hubungi customer service Tamima untuk informasi lebih lanjut.&quot;)
# Footer branding
c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica&quot;, 8)
c.setFillColorRGB(0.5, 0.5, 0.5)
c.drawRightString(width - 50, 30, &quot;Diterbitkan oleh Tamima Hajj &amp; Umrah Service&quot;)
# Simpan PDF
c.showPage()
c.save()
buffer.seek(0)
return buffer
except Exception as e:
st.error(f&quot;Error membuat PDF untuk Order {row.get(&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;, &#x27;Unknown&#x27;)}: {e}&quot;)
raise

# ====================== MAIN APP: UPLOAD EXCEL ======================
st.header(&quot; Upload Data Voucher&quot;)

uploaded_file = st.file_uploader(
&quot;Pilih file Excel (.xlsx)&quot;,
type=[&quot;xlsx&quot;],
help=&quot;File harus memiliki kolom: Order_ID, Nama_Tamu, Properti, Layanan, Check_in, Check_out, Status&quot;,
key=&quot;excel_uploader&quot;
)

if uploaded_file:
try:
# Baca Excel
df = pd.read_excel(uploaded_file)
# Validasi kolom wajib (case-sensitive)
required_columns = [&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;, &#x27;Nama_Tamu&#x27;, &#x27;Properti&#x27;, &#x27;Layanan&#x27;, &#x27;Check_in&#x27;, &#x27;Check_out&#x27;, &#x27;Status&#x27;]
missing_columns = [col for col in required_columns if col not in df.columns]
if missing_columns:
st.error(f&quot; **Kolom tidak ditemukan:** {&#x27;, &#x27;.join(missing_columns)}&quot;)
st.info(&quot;Pastikan file Excel memiliki kolom dengan nama yang tepat (case-sensitive).&quot;)
st.stop()
# Success message dan preview
st.success(f&quot; File berhasil dibaca! Total **{len(df)} voucher** akan dibuat.&quot;)
col1, col2 = st.columns([2, 1])
with col1:
st.subheader(&quot; Preview Data&quot;)
st.dataframe(df.head(), use_container_width=True)
with col2:
st.subheader(&quot; Statistik&quot;)
st.metric(&quot;Total Voucher&quot;, len(df))
st.metric(&quot;Status Unik&quot;, df[&#x27;Status&#x27;].nunique())
st.divider()
# ====================== DOWNLOAD OPTIONS ======================
st.header(&quot; Download Voucher&quot;)
download_option = st.radio(
&quot;Pilih opsi download:&quot;,
[&quot;Single Voucher (Individual)&quot;, &quot;All Vouchers (ZIP File)&quot;],
horizontal=True,
key=&quot;download_option&quot;
)
if download_option == &quot;Single Voucher (Individual)&quot;:
# Dropdown pemilihan
selected_order = st.selectbox(
&quot;Pilih Order ID:&quot;,
options=df[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;].tolist(),
format_func=lambda x: f&quot;{x} - {df[df[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;]==x][&#x27;Nama_Tamu&#x27;].values[0]}&quot;,
key=&quot;select_order&quot;
)
if selected_order:
# Ambil data row yang dipilih
selected_row = df[df[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;] == selected_order].iloc[0]
# Generate PDF
with st.spinner(f&quot;Menghasilkan voucher untuk {selected_row[&#x27;Nama_Tamu&#x27;]}...&quot;):
pdf_file = create_pdf_voucher(selected_row, logo_image)
# Tombol download
file_name = f&quot;Voucher_{selected_row[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;]}.pdf&quot;
st.download_button(
label=f&quot; Download Voucher - {selected_row[&#x27;Nama_Tamu&#x27;]}&quot;,
data=pdf_file,
file_name=file_name,
mime=&quot;application/pdf&quot;,
key=f&quot;download_single_{selected_order}&quot;
)
# Preview info
st.info(f&quot; **Detail:** {selected_row[&#x27;Layanan&#x27;]} | {selected_row[&#x27;Properti&#x27;]} | Status: {selected_row[&#x27;Status&#x27;]}&quot;)
else: # All Vouchers ZIP
st.info(&quot; Proses ini akan menghasilkan file ZIP berisi semua voucher. Gunakan dengan bijak untuk data besar (&gt;100 voucher).&quot;)
if st.button(&quot; Generate &amp; Download ZIP&quot;, type=&quot;primary&quot;, key=&quot;generate_zip_btn&quot;):
if len(df) &gt; 200:
st.warning(&quot; Data lebih dari 200 baris. Proses mungkin memakan waktu beberapa menit.&quot;)
zip_buffer = io.BytesIO()
try:
with zipfile.ZipFile(zip_buffer, &#x27;w&#x27;, zipfile.ZIP_DEFLATED) as zip_file:
progress_bar = st.progress(0)
status_text = st.empty()
for idx, (_, row) in enumerate(df.iterrows()):
# Update status
percent_complete = (idx + 1) / len(df)
status_text.text(f&quot; Memproses {idx + 1}/{len(df)}: {row[&#x27;Nama_Tamu&#x27;]}...&quot;)
progress_bar.progress(percent_complete)
# Generate PDF
pdf_buffer = create_pdf_voucher(row, logo_image)
# Nama file: Voucher_{Order_ID}_{Nama_Tamu}.pdf
safe_name = str(row[&#x27;Nama_Tamu&#x27;]).replace(&quot; &quot;, &quot;_&quot;).replace(&quot;/&quot;, &quot;_&quot;)
file_name = f&quot;Voucher_{row[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;]}_{safe_name}.pdf&quot;
# Tambahkan ke ZIP
zip_file.writestr(file_name, pdf_buffer.getvalue())
# Selesai
status_text.success(f&quot; Berhasil generate {len(df)} voucher!&quot;)
progress_bar.empty()
# Siapkan ZIP untuk download
zip_buffer.seek(0)
st.download_button(
label=f&quot; Download Semua Voucher ({len(df)} file)&quot;,
data=zip_buffer,
file_name=&quot;Tamima_Vouchers.zip&quot;,
mime=&quot;application/zip&quot;,
key=&quot;download_zip_final&quot;
)
except Exception as e:
st.error(f&quot; Gagal membuat ZIP: {e}&quot;)
st.exception(e)
except Exception as e:
st.error(f&quot; Terjadi kesalahan saat membaca file: {e}&quot;)
st.info(&quot;Pastikan file Excel tidak corrupted dan formatnya benar.&quot;)

else:
# State awal
st.info(&quot; Silakan upload file Excel untuk memulai.&quot;)
# Contoh format
with st.expander(&quot; Lihat Format Excel yang Diperlukan&quot;):
st.markdown(&quot;&quot;&quot;
File Excel harus memiliki sheet dengan kolom berikut (case-sensitive):
| Kolom | Contoh Isi |
|-------|-----------|
| Order_ID | ORD-2024-001 |
| Nama_Tamu | Ahmad Fauzi |
| Properti | Hotel Madinah |
| Layanan | Paket Umrah 9 Hari |
| Check_in | 2024-12-01 |
| Check_out | 2024-12-10 |
| Status | Paid |
&quot;&quot;&quot;)
# Buat dummy dataframe untuk contoh
dummy_data = {
&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;: [&#x27;ORD-001&#x27;, &#x27;ORD-002&#x27;],
&#x27;Nama_Tamu&#x27;: [&#x27;Ahmad&#x27;, &#x27;Fatimah&#x27;],
&#x27;Properti&#x27;: [&#x27;Hotel A&#x27;, &#x27;Hotel B&#x27;],
&#x27;Layanan&#x27;: [&#x27;Umrah&#x27;, &#x27;Haji&#x27;],
&#x27;Check_in&#x27;: [&#x27;2024-01-01&#x27;, &#x27;2024-02-01&#x27;],

&#x27;Status&#x27;: [&#x27;Paid&#x27;, &#x27;Pending&#x27;]
}
st.dataframe(pd.DataFrame(dummy_data))

# ====================== FOOTER APP ======================
st.divider()
st.caption(&quot; 2024 Tamima Hajj &amp; Umrah Service - E-Voucher Generator System&quot;)</code></pre></div></div></pre><hr/><h2><strong> Requirements.txt</strong></h2><p>Buat file <code class="code-block_container__lbMX4"><pre class="m-0 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-none px-4 py-3 font-mono text-[#24292e] dark:text-[#e1e4e8]"><code class="text-[11px] leading-normal sm:text-[13px]">import streamlit as st
import pandas as pd
import qrcode
from PIL import Image
from reportlab.pdfgen import canvas
from reportlab.lib.pagesizes import A4
from reportlab.lib.utils import ImageReader
from reportlab.lib import colors
import io
import os
import zipfile

# ====================== KONFIGURASI HALAMAN ======================
st.set_page_config(
page_title=&quot;Tamima E-Voucher Generator&quot;,
page_icon=&quot;&quot;,
layout=&quot;wide&quot;,
initial_sidebar_state=&quot;expanded&quot;
)

# ====================== STYLE CUSTOM ======================
st.markdown(&quot;&quot;&quot;
&lt;style&gt;
.main-header {
font-size: 2.5rem;
font-weight: bold;
color: #1E3A8A;
text-align: center;
margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.stButton&gt;button {
width: 100%;
border-radius: 5px;
font-weight: bold;
}
&lt;/style&gt;
&quot;&quot;&quot;, unsafe_allow_html=True)

# ====================== FUNGSI UTILITAS ======================

def load_logo(logo_option, uploaded_logo_file):
&quot;&quot;&quot;
Memuat logo berdasarkan pilihan user (Default atau Upload Custom).
Returns PIL Image object or None.
&quot;&quot;&quot;
logo_image = None
if logo_option == &quot;Upload Custom&quot;:
if uploaded_logo_file:
try:
logo_image = Image.open(uploaded_logo_file)
except Exception:
st.sidebar.error(&quot;Gagal memuat gambar logo. Pastikan format PNG/JPG.&quot;)
else:
st.sidebar.warning(&quot;Silakan upload file logo.&quot;)
else:
# Default Logo
if os.path.exists(&quot;logo_tamima.png&quot;):
try:
logo_image = Image.open(&quot;logo_tamima.png&quot;)
except Exception:
st.sidebar.warning(&quot;File logo_tamima.png ditemukan tapi rusak.&quot;)
else:
st.sidebar.warning(&quot;File &#x27;logo_tamima.png&#x27; tidak ditemukan di folder proyek.&quot;)
return logo_image

def generate_qr_bytes(data):
&quot;&quot;&quot;
Generate QR Code dan return sebagai BytesIO (in-memory).
&quot;&quot;&quot;
qr = qrcode.QRCode(
version=1,
error_correction=qrcode.constants.ERROR_CORRECT_L,
box_size=10,
border=2
)
qr.add_data(data)
qr.make(fit=True)
img = qr.make_image(fill_color=&quot;black&quot;, back_color=&quot;white&quot;)
buffer = io.BytesIO()
img.save(buffer, format=&#x27;PNG&#x27;)
buffer.seek(0)
return buffer

def create_pdf_voucher(row, logo_image):
&quot;&quot;&quot;
Membuat PDF voucher untuk satu baris data menggunakan ReportLab.
&quot;&quot;&quot;
buffer = io.BytesIO()
c = canvas.Canvas(buffer, pagesize=A4)
width, height = A4
# --- HEADER ---
# Logo
if logo_image:
logo_reader = ImageReader(logo_image)
# Posisi: Kiri Atas (x=50, y=height-100), Ukuran: 100x80
c.drawImage(logo_reader, x=50, y=height - 100, width=100, height=80, preserveAspectRatio=True)
# Judul
c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica-Bold&quot;, 20)
c.setFillColor(colors.HexColor(&quot;#1E3A8A&quot;)) # Biru Tua
c.drawString(160, height - 80, &quot;E-VOUCHER TAMIMA&quot;)
c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica&quot;, 12)
c.setFillColor(colors.black)
c.drawString(160, height - 100, &quot;Hajj &amp; Umrah Service&quot;)
# Garis Pemisah Emas
c.setStrokeColor(colors.HexColor(&quot;#D4AF37&quot;))
c.setLineWidth(2)
c.line(50, height - 115, width - 50, height - 115)
# --- BODY (DETAIL DATA) ---
c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica-Bold&quot;, 11)
c.setFillColor(colors.black)
start_y = height - 150
line_height = 25
# Mapping label dan data
fields = [
(&quot;Order ID&quot;, str(row[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;])),
(&quot;Nama Tamu&quot;, str(row[&#x27;Nama_Tamu&#x27;])),
(&quot;Properti&quot;, str(row[&#x27;Properti&#x27;])),
(&quot;Layanan&quot;, str(row[&#x27;Layanan&#x27;])),
(&quot;Check-in&quot;, str(row[&#x27;Check_in&#x27;])),
(&quot;Check-out&quot;, str(row[&#x27;Check_out&#x27;])),
(&quot;Status&quot;, str(row[&#x27;Status&#x27;]))
]
current_y = start_y
for label, value in fields:
c.drawString(60, current_y, f&quot;{label}:&quot;)
c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica&quot;, 11)
c.drawString(150, current_y, value)
c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica-Bold&quot;, 11)
current_y -= line_height
# --- QR CODE ---
# Format: OrderID:{Order_ID}|Guest:{Nama_Tamu}|Status:{Status}
qr_content = f&quot;OrderID:{row[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;]}|Guest:{row[&#x27;Nama_Tamu&#x27;]}|Status:{row[&#x27;Status&#x27;]}&quot;
qr_buffer = generate_qr_bytes(qr_content)
qr_reader = ImageReader(qr_buffer)
# Posisi QR: Kanan Tengah
qr_size = 120
qr_x = width - 200
qr_y = height - 250
c.drawImage(qr_reader, x=qr_x, y=qr_y, width=qr_size, height=qr_size)
c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica-Oblique&quot;, 9)
c.drawCentredString(qr_x + (qr_size/2), qr_y - 15, &quot;Scan untuk verifikasi&quot;)
# --- FOOTER ---
c.setStrokeColor(colors.lightgrey)
c.setLineWidth(1)
c.line(50, 80, width - 50, 80)
c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica-Oblique&quot;, 9)
c.setFillColor(colors.darkgrey)
c.drawString(50, 60, &quot;Syarat &amp; Ketentuan:&quot;)
c.drawString(50, 45, &quot;1. Voucher berlaku 6 bulan sejak tanggal pembelian.&quot;)
c.drawString(50, 30, &quot;2. Tidak dapat digabung dengan promo lainnya.&quot;)
c.drawString(50, 15, &quot;3. Tunjukkan voucher ini saat check-in.&quot;)
c.showPage()
c.save()
buffer.seek(0)
return buffer

# ====================== APLIKASI UTAMA ======================

def main():
# Judul Utama
st.markdown(&#x27;&lt;p class=&quot;main-header&quot;&gt; Tamima E-Voucher Generator&lt;/p&gt;&#x27;, unsafe_allow_html=True)
st.write(&quot;Unggah file Excel untuk membuat voucher PDF otomatis dengan Logo &amp; QR Code.&quot;)
# --- SIDEBAR PENGATURAN ---
st.sidebar.header(&quot; Pengaturan&quot;)
logo_option = st.sidebar.radio(
&quot;Pilih Sumber Logo:&quot;,
[&quot;Default&quot;, &quot;Upload Custom&quot;],
index=0
)
uploaded_logo_file = None
if logo_option == &quot;Upload Custom&quot;:
uploaded_logo_file = st.sidebar.file_uploader(
&quot;Upload Logo (PNG/JPG)&quot;,
type=[&quot;png&quot;, &quot;jpg&quot;, &quot;jpeg&quot;],
help=&quot;Ukuran disarankan: 500x500 px, background transparan.&quot;
)
logo_image = load_logo(logo_option, uploaded_logo_file)
if logo_image:
st.sidebar.success(&quot;Logo berhasil dimuat.&quot;)
else:
st.sidebar.info(&quot;Voucher akan dibuat tanpa logo.&quot;)
st.sidebar.markdown(&quot;---&quot;)
st.sidebar.write(&quot; 2024 Tamima Hajj &amp; Umrah&quot;)
# --- MAIN CONTENT ---
uploaded_file = st.file_uploader(&quot; Upload File Excel (.xlsx)&quot;, type=[&quot;xlsx&quot;])
if uploaded_file is not None:
try:
# Baca Excel
df = pd.read_excel(uploaded_file)
# Validasi Kolom
required_cols = [&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;, &#x27;Nama_Tamu&#x27;, &#x27;Properti&#x27;, &#x27;Layanan&#x27;, &#x27;Check_in&#x27;, &#x27;Check_out&#x27;, &#x27;Status&#x27;]
missing_cols = [col for col in required_cols if col not in df.columns]
if missing_cols:
st.error(f&quot; **Kolom Tidak Ditemukan:** {&#x27;, &#x27;.join(missing_cols)}&quot;)
st.info(f&quot;Pastikan file Excel memiliki kolom berikut: {&#x27;, &#x27;.join(required_cols)}&quot;)
st.stop()
# Preview Data
st.success(f&quot; File berhasil dibaca! Total **{len(df)}** data voucher.&quot;)
with st.expander(&quot; Preview Data Excel&quot;):
st.dataframe(df, use_container_width=True)
st.markdown(&quot;---&quot;)
st.header(&quot; Opsi Download&quot;)
# Pilihan Mode Download
download_mode = st.radio(
&quot;Pilih metode download:&quot;,
[&quot;Download Single Voucher&quot;, &quot;Download Semua (ZIP)&quot;],
horizontal=True
)
if download_mode == &quot;Download Single Voucher&quot;:
# Pilih Order ID
order_list = df[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;].astype(str).tolist()
selected_order = st.selectbox(
&quot;Pilih Order ID:&quot;,
options=order_list,
index=0
)
# Ambil data baris terpilih
selected_row = df[df[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;].astype(str) == selected_order].iloc[0]
# Generate PDF Preview (Opsional, bisa langsung download)
if st.button(&quot; Generate &amp; Download Voucher Ini&quot;, type=&quot;primary&quot;, key=&quot;btn_single&quot;):
with st.spinner(&quot;Sedang membuat PDF...&quot;):
try:
pdf_buffer = create_pdf_voucher(selected_row, logo_image)
file_name = f&quot;Voucher_{selected_row[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;]}.pdf&quot;
st.download_button(
label=&quot; Klik untuk Download PDF&quot;,
data=pdf_buffer,
file_name=file_name,
mime=&quot;application/pdf&quot;,
key=&quot;download_single_pdf&quot;
)
st.success(&quot;PDF siap diunduh!&quot;)
except Exception as e:
st.error(f&quot;Gagal membuat PDF: {str(e)}&quot;)
else: # Download Semua (ZIP)
st.warning(f&quot; Anda akan membuat **{len(df)}** file PDF dalam satu ZIP. Proses mungkin memakan waktu.&quot;)
if st.button(&quot; Generate &amp; Download ZIP&quot;, type=&quot;primary&quot;, key=&quot;btn_zip&quot;):
zip_buffer = io.BytesIO()
progress_bar = st.progress(0)
status_text = st.empty()
try:
with zipfile.ZipFile(zip_buffer, &#x27;w&#x27;, zipfile.ZIP_DEFLATED) as zip_file:
for idx, row in df.iterrows():
# Update Progress
progress = (idx + 1) / len(df)
progress_bar.progress(progress)
status_text.text(f&quot;Memproses: {row[&#x27;Nama_Tamu&#x27;]} ({idx + 1}/{len(df)})&quot;)
# Generate PDF
pdf_buffer = create_pdf_voucher(row, logo_image)
# Nama file dalam ZIP
# Sanitasi nama file untuk keamanan
safe_name = str(row[&#x27;Nama_Tamu&#x27;]).replace(&#x27;/&#x27;, &#x27;_&#x27;).replace(&#x27;\\&#x27;, &#x27;_&#x27;)
zip_filename = f&quot;Voucher_{row[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;]}_{safe_name}.pdf&quot;
# Masukkan ke ZIP
zip_file.writestr(zip_filename, pdf_buffer.getvalue())
zip_buffer.seek(0)
status_text.success(&quot; Semua voucher berhasil dibuat!&quot;)
progress_bar.empty()
st.download_button(
label=&quot; Download File ZIP&quot;,
data=zip_buffer,
file_name=&quot;Tamima_Vouchers.zip&quot;,
mime=&quot;application/zip&quot;,
key=&quot;download_zip_file&quot;
)
except Exception as e:
st.error(f&quot;Terjadi kesalahan saat membuat ZIP: {str(e)}&quot;)
progress_bar.empty()
except Exception as e:
st.error(f&quot; Gagal membaca file Excel: {str(e)}&quot;)
st.info(&quot;Pastikan file bukan dalam format .csv dan tidak sedang dibuka di aplikasi lain.&quot;)

if __name__ == &quot;__main__&quot;:
main()</code></pre></div></div></pre><h3> File: <code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object <li><strong>Layout Wide &amp; Responsif:</strong> Tampilan rapi di desktop maupun mobile.</li>
<li><strong>Validasi Kolom Excel:</strong> Mencegah error jika kolom kurang.</li>
<li><strong>Logo Dinamis:</strong> Bisa pakai default file atau upload langsung via sidebar.</li>
<li><strong>QR Code In-Memory:</strong> Tidak menyimpan file sampah di server.</li>
<li><strong>Download Fleksibel:</strong> Bisa pilih satu voucher atau download semua sekaligus (ZIP).</li>
<li><strong>Progress Bar:</strong> Indikator loading saat generate banyak voucher.</li>
<li><strong>Error Handling:</strong> Pesan error yang jelas jika file rusak atau proses gagal.</li>

web berbasis <strong>Streamlit</strong> bernama <strong>Tamima EVoucher Generator</strong> untuk membuat dan mencetak <strong>PDF voucher</strong> dari file Excel. Aplikasi harus terlihat rapi (layout wide) dan siap dideploy (Streamlit Community Cloud / HuggingFace Spaces). Ikuti spesifikasi ini:</p><h2>Tujuan</h2><p>User mengunggah file <strong>Excel (.xlsx)</strong> berisi data voucher. Aplikasi menghasilkan <strong>PDF voucher</strong> untuk tiap baris, lengkap dengan <strong>logo Tamima</strong> dan <strong>QR Code</strong>, lalu user bisa mengunduh <strong>satu voucher</strong> atau <strong>semua voucher dalam ZIP</strong>.</p><h2>Input Excel</h2><p>Wajib memiliki kolom berikut (case-sensitive):</p><ul>
<li><code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">Order_ID</code></li>
<li><code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">Nama_Tamu</code></li>
<li><code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">Properti</code></li>
<li><code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">Layanan</code></li>
<li><code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">Check_in</code></li>
<li><code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">Check_out</code></li>
<li><code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">Status</code></li>
</ul><p>Jika ada kolom yang hilang, tampilkan error yang jelas dan hentikan proses.</p><h2>UI/UX</h2><ul>
<li><code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">st.set_page_config(page_title=&quot;Tamima E-Voucher Generator&quot;, layout=&quot;wide&quot;)</code></li>
<li>Judul utama: Tamima EVoucher Generator</li>
<li>Sidebar Pengaturan:<!-- -->
<ul>
<li>pilihan logo: <strong>Default</strong> atau <strong>Upload Custom</strong></li>
<li>jika Default: gunakan file <code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">logo_tamima.png</code> yang berada di folder proyek; jika tidak ada, tampilkan peringatan dan minta user upload.</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Area utama:<!-- -->
<ol>
<li>Upload Excel</li>
<li>Tampilkan preview dataframe (head)</li>
<li>Opsi download:<!-- -->
<ul>
<li><strong>Single Voucher</strong>: pilih <code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">Order_ID</code> dari dropdown, lalu tombol download PDF</li>
<li><strong>All Vouchers (ZIP)</strong>: tombol Generate &amp; Download ZIP + progress bar</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
</li>
</ul><h2>PDF Voucher (ReportLab)</h2><p>Gunakan ukuran A4. Buat desain voucher seperti ini:</p><ul>
<li>Header:<!-- -->
<ul>
<li>tampilkan <strong>logo</strong> di kiri atas (sekitar 100x80, preserve aspect ratio)</li>
<li>judul: EVOUCHER TAMIMA + subjudul Hajj &amp; Umrah Service</li>
<li>garis pemisah warna emas</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Body:<!-- -->
<ul>
<li>tampilkan detail: Order ID, Nama Tamu, Properti, Layanan, Check-in, Check-out, Status</li>
<li>pastikan semua value di-cast ke string</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>QR Code:<!-- -->
<ul>
<li>konten QR: <code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">OrderID:{Order_ID}|Guest:{Nama_Tamu}|Status:{Status}</code></li>
<li>QR harus dibuat <strong>in-memory</strong> (BytesIO), <strong>tanpa menyimpan file permanen ke disk</strong></li>
<li>temp file boleh dipakai hanya jika benar-benar diperlukan oleh ReportLab, tapi harus segera dihapus</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Footer:<!-- -->
<ul>
<li>syarat &amp; ketentuan (contoh): berlaku 6 bulan, tidak bisa digabung promo</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul><h2>Output</h2><ul>
<li>Single: download <code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">Voucher_{Order_ID}.pdf</code></li>
<li>ZIP: <code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">Tamima_Vouchers.zip</code> berisi semua voucher: <code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">Voucher_{Order_ID}_{Nama_Tamu}.pdf</code></li>
</ul><h2>Kualitas &amp; Keamanan</h2><ul>
<li>Tangani exception saat baca Excel dan saat generate PDF.</li>
<li>Pastikan tidak ada konflik key pada widget Streamlit (gunakan key unik).</li>
<li>Jangan gunakan penyimpanan file QR permanen.</li>
<li>Kode harus lengkap dalam satu file <code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">app.py</code>.</li>
</ul><h2>Tambahan</h2><p>Sertakan contoh <code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">requirements.txt</code> minimal:</p><ul>
<li>streamlit</li>
<li>pandas</li>
<li>qrcode</li>
<li>Pillow</li>
<li>reportlab</li>
</ul><p>Hasil akhir yang saya minta: <strong>Generate kode lengkap <code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">app.py</code></strong> sesuai spesifikasi di atas.</p></div></div></div></div><h2 id="radix-_R_567j6r5bsnpfcnpl5umml9fivbH1_" class="text-lg font-semibold leading-none tracking-tight <strong>versi final</strong> dari aplikasi <strong>E-Voucher Generator dengan Logo Tamima</strong> yang siap di-deploy sebagai <strong>Web App AI</strong> (Streamlit + Logo + QR Code + PDF Generator).</p><hr/><h2><strong> Final Code (Streamlit Web App)</strong></h2><pre><div class="not-prose my-0 flex w-full flex-col overflow-clip border border-border text-text-primary rounded-lg not-prose relative" data-code-block="true"><div class="border-border flex items-center justify-between border-b px-4 py-2"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg width="14" stroke-width="1.5" 19.0011C6.00001 17.4501 6.00001 15.3443 6 14C6 13 4.5 12 4.5 12C4.5 12 6.00001 11 6.00001 10C6.00001 8.827 6.00001 6.62207 6.00001 4.99914C6.00001 3.89457 6.89544 3 8.00001 3L9.00001 3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M15 21L16 21C17.1046 21 18 20.1057 18 19.0011C18 17.4501 18 15.3443 18 14C18 13 19.5 12 19.5 12C19.5 12 18 11 18 10C18 8.827 18 6.62207 18 4.99914C18 3.89457 17.1046 3 16 3L15 3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg><span class="text-text-secondary text-sm font-medium">Python</span></div><button class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-surface-primary disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 text-sm text-interactive-active hover:text-interactive-normal active:text-text-tertiary font-normal relative rounded-lg p-[6px]" type="button" data-state="closed" data-slot="tooltip-trigger"><svg width="16" height="16" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" color="currentColor" class="text-interactive-positive absolute inset-0 m-auto rotate-90 opacity-0 transition-all duration-300"><path d="M5 13L9 17L19 7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg><svg width="16" height="16" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" color="currentColor" class="absolute inset-0 m-auto opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"><path d="M19.4 20H9.6C9.26863 20 9 19.7314 9 19.4V9.6C9 9.26863 9.26863 9 9.6 9H19.4C19.7314 9 20 9.26863 20 9.6V19.4C20 19.7314 19.7314 20 19.4 20Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M15 9V4.6C15 4.26863 14.7314 4 14.4 4H4.6C4.26863 4 4 4.26863 4 4.6V14.4C4 14.7314 4.26863 15 4.6 15H9" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></button></div><div class="code-block_container__lbMX4"><pre class="m-0 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-none px-4 py-3 font-mono text-[#24292e] dark:text-[#e1e4e8]"><code class="text-[11px] leading-normal sm:text-[13px]">import streamlit as st
import pandas as pd
import qrcode
from PIL import Image
from reportlab.pdfgen import canvas
from reportlab.lib.pagesizes import A4
from reportlab.lib.utils import ImageReader
import io
import os
import zipfile
import base64

# ====================== KONFIGURASI ======================
st.set_page_config(
page_title=&quot;Tamima E-Voucher Generator&quot;,
page_icon=&quot;&quot;,
layout=&quot;wide&quot;
)

# Judul Aplikasi
st.title(&quot; **Tamima E-Voucher Generator**&quot;)
st.markdown(&quot;&quot;&quot;
&lt;style&gt;
.stButton&gt;button {
background-color: #4CAF50;
color: white;
padding: 10px 24px;
border-radius: 5px;
border: none;
}
.stButton&gt;button:hover {
background-color: #45a049;
}
&lt;/style&gt;
&quot;&quot;&quot;, unsafe_allow_html=True)

# Upload Logo Tamima (default atau custom)
st.sidebar.header(&quot; Pengaturan&quot;)
logo_option = st.sidebar.radio(&quot;Pilih Logo:&quot;, [&quot;Default&quot;, &quot;Upload Custom&quot;])

if logo_option == &quot;Upload Custom&quot;:
logo_file = st.sidebar.file_uploader(&quot;Upload Logo Tamima (PNG/JPG)&quot;, type=[&quot;png&quot;, &quot;jpg&quot;, &quot;jpeg&quot;])
if logo_file:
logo_image = Image.open(logo_file)
else:
logo_image = None
else:
# Logo default (simpan di folder yang sama)
try:
logo_image = Image.open(&quot;logo_tamima.png&quot;)
except FileNotFoundError:
logo_image = None
st.sidebar.warning(&quot;Logo default tidak ditemukan. Silakan upload logo.&quot;)

# ====================== FUNGSI ======================
def generate_qr_bytes(data):
&quot;&quot;&quot;Generate QR Code dan return sebagai bytes (tanpa menyimpan file)&quot;&quot;&quot;
qr = qrcode.QRCode(
version=1,
error_correction=qrcode.constants.ERROR_CORRECT_L,
box_size=10,
border=2
)
qr.add_data(data)
qr.make(fit=True)
img = qr.make_image(fill_color=&quot;black&quot;, back_color=&quot;white&quot;)

buffer = io.BytesIO()
img.save(buffer, format=&#x27;PNG&#x27;)
buffer.seek(0)
return buffer

def create_pdf(row, logo_image):
&quot;&quot;&quot;Buat PDF voucher untuk satu baris data&quot;&quot;&quot;
buffer = io.BytesIO()
c = canvas.Canvas(buffer, pagesize=A4)
width, height = A4

# === HEADER (Logo + Judul) ===
if logo_image:
logo_reader = ImageReader(logo_image)
c.drawImage(logo_reader, x=50, y=height - 100, width=100, height=80, preserveAspectRatio=True)

c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica-Bold&quot;, 18)
c.drawString(160, height - 80, &quot;E-VOUCHER TAMIMA&quot;)
c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica&quot;, 12)
c.drawString(160, height - 100, &quot;Hajj &amp; Umrah Service&quot;)

# Garis pemisah
c.setStrokeColorRGB(0.8, 0.6, 0.2) # Warna emas
c.setLineWidth(2)
c.line(50, height - 110, width - 50, height - 110)

# === DETAIL VOUCHER ===
c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica-Bold&quot;, 12)
y = height - 140
details = [
(&quot;Order ID&quot;, row[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;]),
(&quot;Nama Tamu&quot;, row[&#x27;Nama_Tamu&#x27;]),
(&quot;Properti&quot;, row[&#x27;Properti&#x27;]),
(&quot;Layanan&quot;, row[&#x27;Layanan&#x27;]),
(&quot;Check-in&quot;, str(row[&#x27;Check_in&#x27;])),
(&quot;Check-out&quot;, str(row[&#x27;Check_out&#x27;])),
(&quot;Status&quot;, row[&#x27;Status&#x27;])
]

for label, value in details:
c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica-Bold&quot;, 11)
c.drawString(60, y, f&quot;{label}:&quot;)
c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica&quot;, 11)
c.drawString(160, y, str(value))
y -= 25

# === QR CODE ===
qr_content = f&quot;OrderID:{row[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;]}|Guest:{row[&#x27;Nama_Tamu&#x27;]}|Status:{row[&#x27;Status&#x27;]}&quot;
qr_buffer = generate_qr_bytes(qr_content)

# Simpan sementara untuk reportlab
temp_qr = f&quot;temp_qr_{row[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;]}.png&quot;
with open(temp_qr, &quot;wb&quot;) as f:
f.write(qr_buffer.getvalue())

c.drawImage(temp_qr, width - 200, height - 250, width=120, height=120)
c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica&quot;, 9)
c.drawString(width - 180, height - 265, &quot;Scan untuk verifikasi&quot;)

# Hapus file QR sementara
os.remove(temp_qr)

# === FOOTER ===
c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica-Oblique&quot;, 9)
c.drawString(60, 50, &quot;Syarat &amp; Ketentuan:&quot;)
c.drawString(60, 35, &quot; Voucher berlaku 6 bulan sejak tanggal pembelian.&quot;)
c.drawString(60, 20, &quot; Tidak dapat digabung dengan promo lainnya.&quot;)

c.showPage()
c.save()
buffer.seek(0)
return buffer

# ====================== MAIN APP ======================
st.header(&quot; Upload Data Voucher&quot;)
uploaded_file = st.file_uploader(&quot;Pilih file Excel (.xlsx)&quot;, type=[&quot;xlsx&quot;])

if uploaded_file:
try:
df = pd.read_excel(uploaded_file)

# Validasi kolom
required_cols = [&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;, &#x27;Nama_Tamu&#x27;, &#x27;Properti&#x27;, &#x27;Layanan&#x27;, &#x27;Check_in&#x27;, &#x27;Check_out&#x27;, &#x27;Status&#x27;]
missing_cols = [col for col in required_cols if col not in df.columns]

if missing_cols:
st.error(f&quot; Kolom yang hilang: **{&#x27;, &#x27;.join(missing_cols)}**&quot;)
st.info(&quot;Pastikan file Excel memiliki semua kolom yang diperlukan.&quot;)
else:
st.success(f&quot; File berhasil dibaca! Total: **{len(df)} voucher**&quot;)
st.dataframe(df.head(), use_container_width=True)

# Pilihan download
st.header(&quot; Download Voucher&quot;)
download_option = st.radio(&quot;Pilih opsi download:&quot;, [&quot;Single Voucher&quot;, &quot;All Vouchers (ZIP)&quot;])

if download_option == &quot;Single Voucher&quot;:
selected_order = st.selectbox(
&quot;Pilih Order ID:&quot;,
options=df[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;].tolist(),
format_func=lambda x: f&quot;{x} - {df[df[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;]==x][&#x27;Nama_Tamu&#x27;].values[0]}&quot;
)

if selected_order:
selected_row = df[df[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;] == selected_order].iloc[0]
pdf_file = create_pdf(selected_row, logo_image)

st.download_button(
label=f&quot; Download Voucher - {selected_row[&#x27;Nama_Tamu&#x27;]}&quot;,
data=pdf_file,
file_name=f&quot;Voucher_{selected_row[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;]}.pdf&quot;,
mime=&quot;application/pdf&quot;,
key=f&quot;single_download_{selected_order}&quot;
)

else: # All Vouchers (ZIP)
if st.button(&quot; Generate &amp; Download ZIP&quot;, type=&quot;primary&quot;):
zip_buffer = io.BytesIO()

with zipfile.ZipFile(zip_buffer, &#x27;w&#x27;, zipfile.ZIP_DEFLATED) as zip_file:
progress_bar = st.progress(0)
status_text = st.empty()

for idx, row in df.iterrows():
status_text.text(f&quot;Generating voucher {idx + 1}/{len(df)}...&quot;)
pdf_file = create_pdf(row, logo_image)
zip_file.writestr(
f&quot;Voucher_{row[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;]}_{row[&#x27;Nama_Tamu&#x27;]}.pdf&quot;,
pdf_file.getvalue()
)
progress_bar.progress((idx + 1) / len(df))

zip_buffer.seek(0)
status_text.success(f&quot; Berhasil generate {len(df)} voucher!&quot;)

st.download_button(
label=&quot; Download Semua Voucher (ZIP)&quot;,
data=zip_buffer,
file_name=&quot;Tamima_Vouchers.zip&quot;,
mime=&quot;application/zip&quot;
)

except Exception as e:
st.error(f&quot; Terjadi kesalahan: {str(e)}&quot;)
st.info(&quot;Pastikan format file Excel sudah benar.&quot;)</code></pre></div></div></pre><hr/><h2><strong> Cara Deploy ke Web (Streamlit Cloud / Hugging Face)</strong></h2><ol>

disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 text-sm text-interactive-active hover:text-interactive-normal active:text-text-tertiary font-normal relative rounded-lg p-[6px]" type="button" data-state="closed" data-slot="tooltip-trigger"><svg width="16" height="16" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" m-auto opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"><path d="M19.4 20H9.6C9.26863 20 9 19.7314 9 19.4V9.6C9 9.26863 9.26863 9 9.6 9H19.4C19.7314 9 20 9.26863 20 9.6V19.4C20 19.7314 19.7314 20 19.4 20Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M15 9V4.6C15 4.26863 14.7314 4 14.4 4H4.6C4.26863 4 4 4.26863 4 4.6V14.4C4 14.7314 4.26863 15 4.6 15H9" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></button></div><div class="code-block_container__lbMX4"><pre class="m-0 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-none px-4 py-3 font-mono text-[#24292e] dark:text-[#e1e4e8]"><code class="text-[11px] leading-normal sm:text-[13px]">import streamlit as st
import pandas as pd
import qrcode
from PIL import Image
from reportlab.pdfgen import canvas
from reportlab.lib.pagesizes import A4
from reportlab.lib.utils import ImageReader
import io
import os

# ====================== KONFIGURASI ======================
st.title(&quot; E-Voucher Generator &amp; Printer - Tamima&quot;)
st.write(&quot;Unggah file Excel untuk generate voucher otomatis dengan QR Code &amp; Logo Tamima&quot;)

# Upload Logo (default menggunakan logo yang Anda kirim)
logo_file = st.sidebar.file_uploader(&quot;Upload Logo Tamima (PNG/JPG)&quot;, type=[&quot;png&quot;, &quot;jpg&quot;, &quot;jpeg&quot;], help=&quot;Disarankan ukuran 500x500 px atau lebih&quot;)

if logo_file is None:
st.sidebar.info(&quot;Logo default akan digunakan jika tidak diupload&quot;)
# Anda bisa menaruh logo di folder yang sama dengan nama logo_tamima.png
try:
logo_image = Image.open(&quot;logo_tamima.png&quot;)
except FileNotFoundError:
logo_image = None
st.sidebar.warning(&quot;Logo tidak ditemukan. Silakan upload logo.&quot;)
else:
logo_image = Image.open(logo_file)

# ====================== FUNGSI ======================
def generate_qr_bytes(data):
qr = qrcode.QRCode(box_size=10, border=2)
qr.add_data(data)
qr.make(fit=True)
img = qr.make_image(fill_color=&quot;black&quot;, back_color=&quot;white&quot;)
buffer = io.BytesIO()
img.save(buffer, format=&#x27;PNG&#x27;)
buffer.seek(0)
return buffer

def create_pdf(row, logo_image):
buffer = io.BytesIO()
c = canvas.Canvas(buffer, pagesize=A4)
width, height = A4

# === LOGO TAMIMA ===
if logo_image:
logo_reader = ImageReader(logo_image)
# Logo di tengah atas
c.drawImage(logo_reader, x=width/2 - 90, y=height - 110,
width=180, height=90, preserveAspectRatio=True, mask=&#x27;auto&#x27;)

# === JUDUL VOUCHER ===
c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica-Bold&quot;, 18)
c.drawString(100, height - 150, &quot;E-VOUCHER&quot;)

# Garis pemisah
c.setStrokeColorRGB(0.8, 0.6, 0.2)
c.setLineWidth(2)
c.line(100, height - 160, 500, height - 160)

# === DETAIL VOUCHER ===
c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica&quot;, 11)
y = height - 190
details = [
f&quot;Properti : {row[&#x27;Properti&#x27;]}&quot;,
f&quot;Order ID : {row[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;]}&quot;,
f&quot;Nama Tamu : {row[&#x27;Nama_Tamu&#x27;]}&quot;,
f&quot;Layanan : {row[&#x27;Layanan&#x27;]}&quot;,
f&quot;Periode : {row[&#x27;Check_in&#x27;]} s/d {row[&#x27;Check_out&#x27;]}&quot;,
f&quot;Status : {row[&#x27;Status&#x27;]}&quot;,
]
for line in details:
c.drawString(100, y, line)
y -= 22

# === QR CODE ===
qr_content = f&quot;ID:{row[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;]} | Status:{row[&#x27;Status&#x27;]}&quot;
qr_buffer = generate_qr_bytes(qr_content)
# Simpan sementara untuk reportlab
temp_qr = f&quot;temp_qr_{row[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;]}.png&quot;
with open(temp_qr, &quot;wb&quot;) as f:
f.write(qr_buffer.getvalue())
c.drawImage(temp_qr, 400, height - 240, width=130, height=130)
os.remove(temp_qr)

# === FOOTER ===
c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica-Oblique&quot;, 9)
c.drawString(100, 80, &quot;Syarat &amp; Ketentuan berlaku.&quot;)
c.drawString(100, 65, &quot;Voucher ini diterbitkan oleh Tamima Hajj &amp; Umrah Service&quot;)
c.drawString(100, 50, &quot;Berlaku 6 bulan sejak tanggal pembelian.&quot;)

c.showPage()
c.save()
buffer.seek(0)
return buffer

# ====================== MAIN APP ======================
uploaded_file = st.file_uploader(&quot;Pilih file Excel (.xlsx)&quot;, type=[&quot;xlsx&quot;])

if uploaded_file:
df = pd.read_excel(uploaded_file)
required_cols = [&#x27;Properti&#x27;, &#x27;Order_ID&#x27;, &#x27;Nama_Tamu&#x27;, &#x27;Layanan&#x27;, &#x27;Check_in&#x27;, &#x27;Check_out&#x27;, &#x27;Status&#x27;]
if missing := [col for col in required_cols if col not in df.columns]:
st.error(f&quot;Kolom berikut tidak ditemukan: {missing}&quot;)
st.stop()

st.success(f&quot; File berhasil dibaca! Total {len(df)} voucher akan dibuat.&quot;)
st.dataframe(df.head(), use_container_width=True)

if st.button(&quot; Generate Semua E-Voucher&quot;, type=&quot;primary&quot;):
progress_bar = st.progress(0)
status_text = st.empty()
pdf_list = []
name_list = []

for idx, row in df.iterrows():
status_text.text(f&quot; Sedang memproses: {row[&#x27;Nama_Tamu&#x27;]}...&quot;)
pdf_buffer = create_pdf(row, logo_image)
pdf_list.append(pdf_buffer)
name_list.append(f&quot;Voucher_{row[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;]}_{row[&#x27;Nama_Tamu&#x27;]}.pdf&quot;)
progress_bar.progress((idx + 1) / len(df))

status_text.success(&quot; Semua voucher berhasil dibuat!&quot;)
progress_bar.empty()

# Pilih voucher untuk di-download
selected = st.selectbox(
&quot;Pilih Voucher yang ingin di-download:&quot;,
range(len(df)),
format_func=lambda i: f&quot;{df.iloc[i][&#x27;Nama_Tamu&#x27;]} {df.iloc[i][&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;]}&quot;
)

st.download_button(
label=&quot; Download Voucher Terpilih&quot;,
data=pdf_list[selected],
file_name=name_list[selected],
mime=&quot;application/pdf&quot;
)</code></pre></div></div></pre><hr/><h3>Cara Menggunakan Logo:</h3><ol>
<li>Simpan logo yang Anda kirim sebagai file bernama <strong><code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">logo_tamima.png</code></strong> di folder yang sama dengan aplikasi Streamlit.</li>
<li>Atau langsung upload logo melalui sidebar (lebih fleksibel).</li>
</ol><p><strong>Rekomendasi</strong>: Simpan logo sebagai PNG dengan background transparan agar tampilan lebih bersih.</p><hr/><p>Apakah Anda ingin saya ubah posisi logo (misalnya ke kiri atas, atau lebih besar)? Atau tambahkan nomor voucher / barcode juga? Silakan beri tahu!</p></div></div></div></div><h2 id="radix-_R_4mfj6r5bsnpfcnpl5umml9fivbH1_" class="text-lg font-semibold leading-none tracking-tight hidden">Message from <!-- xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" color="currentColor" class="absolute inset-0 m-auto opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"><path d="M19.4 20H9.6C9.26863 20 9 19.7314 9 19.4V9.6C9 9.26863 class="code-block_container__lbMX4"><pre class="m-0 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-none px-4 py-3 font-mono text-[#24292e] dark:text-[#e1e4e8]"><code class="text-[11px] leading-normal sm:text-[13px]">import streamlit as st
import pandas as pd
import qrcode
from PIL import Image
from reportlab.pdfgen import canvas
from reportlab.lib.pagesizes import A4
import io
import os

# Judul Aplikasi
st.title(&quot; E-Voucher Generator &amp; Printer&quot;)
st.write(&quot;Unggah file Excel Anda untuk mencetak voucher otomatis dengan QR Code.&quot;)

# Upload File Excel
uploaded_file = st.file_uploader(&quot;Pilih file Excel (.xlsx)&quot;, type=[&quot;xlsx&quot;])

def generate_qr_bytes(data):
&quot;&quot;&quot;Generate QR dan kembalikan sebagai BytesIO (tanpa save ke disk)&quot;&quot;&quot;
qr = qrcode.QRCode(box_size=10, border=2)
qr.add_data(data)
qr.make(fit=True)
img = qr.make_image(fill_color=&quot;black&quot;, back_color=&quot;white&quot;)
# Convert ke BytesIO
buffer = io.BytesIO()
img.save(buffer, format=&#x27;PNG&#x27;)
buffer.seek(0)
return buffer

def create_pdf(row):
buffer = io.BytesIO()
c = canvas.Canvas(buffer, pagesize=A4)
width, height = A4
# Header Voucher
c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica-Bold&quot;, 16)
c.drawString(100, height - 80, f&quot;E-VOUCHER: {row[&#x27;Properti&#x27;]}&quot;)
# Detail Data
c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica&quot;, 12)
c.drawString(100, height - 120, f&quot;Order ID: {row[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;]}&quot;)
c.drawString(100, height - 140, f&quot;Nama Tamu: {row[&#x27;Nama_Tamu&#x27;]}&quot;)
c.drawString(100, height - 160, f&quot;Layanan: {row[&#x27;Layanan&#x27;]}&quot;)
c.drawString(100, height - 180, f&quot;Periode: {row[&#x27;Check_in&#x27;]} s/d {row[&#x27;Check_out&#x27;]}&quot;)
c.drawString(100, height - 200, f&quot;Status: {row[&#x27;Status&#x27;]}&quot;)
# Generate QR Status Pembayaran (langsung dari memory)
qr_content = f&quot;ID:{row[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;]} | Status:{row[&#x27;Status&#x27;]}&quot;
qr_buffer = generate_qr_bytes(qr_content)
# Simpan QR ke file sementara (reportlab butuh path)
temp_qr_path = f&quot;temp_qr_{row[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;]}.png&quot;
with open(temp_qr_path, &#x27;wb&#x27;) as f:
f.write(qr_buffer.getvalue())
# Masukkan QR ke PDF
c.drawImage(temp_qr_path, 400, height - 200, width=120, height=120)
# Hapus file QR sementara
os.remove(temp_qr_path)
# Footer S&amp;K
c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica-Oblique&quot;, 10)
c.drawString(100, height - 280, &quot;Syarat &amp; Ketentuan: Berlaku 6 bulan setelah pembelian.&quot;)
c.showPage()
c.save()
buffer.seek(0)
return buffer

if uploaded_file:
df = pd.read_excel(uploaded_file)
# Validasi kolom wajib
required_columns = [&#x27;Properti&#x27;, &#x27;Order_ID&#x27;, &#x27;Nama_Tamu&#x27;, &#x27;Layanan&#x27;, &#x27;Check_in&#x27;, &#x27;Check_out&#x27;, &#x27;Status&#x27;]
missing_cols = [col for col in required_columns if col not in df.columns]
if missing_cols:
st.error(f&quot; Kolom tidak ditemukan: {&#x27;, &#x27;.join(missing_cols)}&quot;)
st.stop()
st.write(&quot; **Preview Data:**&quot;, df.head())
st.write(f&quot;Total voucher: **{len(df)}**&quot;)
if st.button(&quot; Generate Semua E-Voucher&quot;, type=&quot;primary&quot;):
progress_bar = st.progress(0)
status_text = st.empty()
pdf_buffers = []
filenames = []
for index, row in df.iterrows():
status_text.text(f&quot;Memproses: {row[&#x27;Nama_Tamu&#x27;]} ({index+1}/{len(df)})&quot;)
pdf_buffer = create_pdf(row)
pdf_buffers.append(pdf_buffer)
filenames.append(f&quot;Voucher_{row[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;]}.pdf&quot;)
progress_bar.progress((index + 1) / len(df))
status_text.success(&quot; Selesai! Pilih voucher untuk didownload:&quot;)
progress_bar.empty()
# Tampilkan dropdown untuk download individual
selected_idx = st.selectbox(
&quot;Pilih voucher:&quot;,
range(len(df)),
format_func=lambda i: f&quot;{df.iloc[i][&#x27;Nama_Tamu&#x27;]} - {df.iloc[i][&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;]}&quot;
)
st.download_button(
label=f&quot; Download Voucher - {df.iloc[selected_idx][&#x27;Nama_Tamu&#x27;]}&quot;,
data=pdf_buffers[selected_idx],
file_name=filenames[selected_idx],
mime=&quot;application/pdf&quot;
)
# Opsi download ZIP (opsional - perlu library zipfile)
st.info(&quot; Tip: Untuk download semua sekaligus, gunakan fitur ZIP di bawah (coming soon)&quot;)</code></pre></div></div></pre><h2> <strong>Fitur Perbaikan:</strong></h2><div font-mono text-[#24292e] dark:text-[#e1e4e8]"><code class="text-[11px] leading-normal sm:text-[13px]"># Opsi 1: Download semua sebagai ZIP
import zipfile
def create_zip(pdf_buffers, filenames):
zip_buffer = io.BytesIO()
with zipfile.ZipFile(zip_buffer, &#x27;w&#x27;) as zip_file:
for buffer, name in zip(pdf_buffers, filenames):
zip_file.writestr(name, buffer.getvalue())
zip_buffer.seek(0)
return zip_buffer

# Opsi 2: Template kustom
st.sidebar.header(&quot; Pengaturan&quot;)
font_size = st.sidebar.slider(&quot;Ukuran Font&quot;, 8, 20, 12)

xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" color="currentColor" class="absolute inset-0 m-auto opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"><path d="M19.4 20H9.6C9.26863 20 9 19.7314 9 19.4V9.6C9 9.26863 4 14.4 4H4.6C4.26863 4 4 4.26863 4 4.6V14.4C4 14.7314 4.26863 15 4.6 15H9" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></button></div><div class="code-block_container__lbMX4"><pre class="m-0 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-none px-4 py-3 font-mono text-[#24292e] dark:text-[#e1e4e8]"><code class="text-[11px] leading-normal sm:text-[13px]">import streamlit as st
import pandas as pd
import qrcode
from PIL import Image
from reportlab.pdfgen import canvas
from reportlab.lib.pagesizes import A4
from reportlab.lib.utils import ImageReader
import io
import zipfile

# Judul Aplikasi
st.title(&quot; E-Voucher Generator &amp; Printer&quot;)
st.write(&quot;Unggah file Excel Anda untuk mencetak voucher otomatis dengan QR Code.&quot;)

# Contoh format Excel
with st.expander(&quot; Lihat Format Excel yang Diperlukan&quot;):
st.markdown(&quot;&quot;&quot;
| Order_ID | Nama_Tamu | Properti | Layanan | Check_in | Check_out | Status |
|----------|-----------|----------|---------|----------|-----------|--------|
| ORD001 | John Doe | Hotel ABC | Deluxe Room | 2024-01-15 | 2024-01-17 | LUNAS |
&quot;&quot;&quot;)

# Upload File Excel
uploaded_file = st.file_uploader(&quot;Pilih file Excel (.xlsx)&quot;, type=[&quot;xlsx&quot;])

def generate_qr(data):
&quot;&quot;&quot;Generate QR code dan return sebagai PIL Image&quot;&quot;&quot;
qr = qrcode.QRCode(
version=1,
error_correction=qrcode.constants.ERROR_CORRECT_L,
box_size=10,
border=2
)
qr.add_data(data)
qr.make(fit=True)
img = qr.make_image(fill_color=&quot;black&quot;, back_color=&quot;white&quot;)
return img

def create_pdf(row):
&quot;&quot;&quot;Buat PDF voucher untuk satu baris data&quot;&quot;&quot;
buffer = io.BytesIO()
c = canvas.Canvas(buffer, pagesize=A4)
width, height = A4
# ===== HEADER VOUCHER =====
c.setFillColorRGB(0.2, 0.4, 0.8) # Warna biru
c.rect(50, height - 100, width - 100, 60, fill=True)
c.setFillColorRGB(1, 1, 1) # Warna putih
c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica-Bold&quot;, 20)
c.drawCentredString(width / 2, height - 70, f&quot;E-VOUCHER&quot;)
# ===== NAMA PROPERTI =====
c.setFillColorRGB(0, 0, 0)
c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica-Bold&quot;, 16)
c.drawString(60, height - 140, f&quot; {row[&#x27;Properti&#x27;]}&quot;)
# ===== GARIS PEMISAH =====
c.line(60, height - 155, width - 60, height - 155)
# ===== DETAIL DATA =====
c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica&quot;, 12)
y_position = height - 180
details = [
(&quot;Order ID&quot;, row[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;]),
(&quot;Nama Tamu&quot;, row[&#x27;Nama_Tamu&#x27;]),
(&quot;Layanan&quot;, row[&#x27;Layanan&#x27;]),
(&quot;Check-in&quot;, str(row[&#x27;Check_in&#x27;])),
(&quot;Check-out&quot;, str(row[&#x27;Check_out&#x27;])),
(&quot;Status&quot;, row[&#x27;Status&#x27;])
]
for label, value in details:
c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica-Bold&quot;, 11)
c.drawString(60, y_position, f&quot;{label}:&quot;)
c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica&quot;, 11)
c.drawString(160, y_position, str(value))
y_position -= 25
# ===== STATUS BADGE =====
status = str(row[&#x27;Status&#x27;]).upper()
if status == &quot;LUNAS&quot;:
c.setFillColorRGB(0.2, 0.7, 0.3) # Hijau
else:
c.setFillColorRGB(0.9, 0.3, 0.2) # Merah
c.roundRect(60, y_position - 10, 100, 25, 5, fill=True)
c.setFillColorRGB(1, 1, 1)
c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica-Bold&quot;, 10)
c.drawCentredString(110, y_position - 2, status)
# ===== GENERATE QR CODE (IN MEMORY - TANPA SIMPAN FILE) =====
qr_content = f&quot;OrderID:{row[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;]}|Guest:{row[&#x27;Nama_Tamu&#x27;]}|Status:{row[&#x27;Status&#x27;]}&quot;
qr_img = generate_qr(qr_content)
# Convert QR ke bytes (tidak menyimpan ke file)
qr_buffer = io.BytesIO()
qr_img.save(qr_buffer, format=&#x27;PNG&#x27;)
qr_buffer.seek(0)
# Gunakan ImageReader untuk embed QR ke PDF
qr_image_reader = ImageReader(qr_buffer)
c.drawImage(qr_image_reader, width - 180, height - 320, width=120, height=120)
# Label QR
c.setFillColorRGB(0, 0, 0)
c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica&quot;, 8)
c.drawCentredString(width - 120, height - 335, &quot;Scan untuk verifikasi&quot;)
# ===== FOOTER S&amp;K =====
c.setFillColorRGB(0.9, 0.9, 0.9)
c.rect(50, 80, width - 100, 60, fill=True)
c.setFillColorRGB(0.3, 0.3, 0.3)
c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica-Bold&quot;, 9)
c.drawString(60, 120, &quot;Syarat &amp; Ketentuan:&quot;)
c.setFont(&quot;Helvetica&quot;, 8)
c.drawString(60, 105, &quot; Voucher berlaku 6 bulan setelah tanggal pembelian&quot;)
c.drawString(60, 92, &quot; Tidak dapat digabung dengan promo lainnya&quot;)
c.showPage()
c.save()
buffer.seek(0)
return buffer

# ===== MAIN LOGIC =====
if uploaded_file:
try:
df = pd.read_excel(uploaded_file)
# Validasi kolom yang diperlukan
required_cols = [&#x27;Properti&#x27;, &#x27;Order_ID&#x27;, &#x27;Nama_Tamu&#x27;, &#x27;Layanan&#x27;, &#x27;Check_in&#x27;, &#x27;Check_out&#x27;, &#x27;Status&#x27;]
missing_cols = [col for col in required_cols if col not in df.columns]
if missing_cols:
st.error(f&quot; Kolom yang hilang: **{&#x27;, &#x27;.join(missing_cols)}**&quot;)
st.info(&quot;Pastikan file Excel Anda memiliki semua kolom yang diperlukan.&quot;)
else:
st.success(f&quot; File berhasil dibaca! Total: **{len(df)} data**&quot;)
st.write(&quot;### Preview Data:&quot;)
st.dataframe(df.head(10), use_container_width=True)
col1, col2 = st.columns(2)
with col1:
if st.button(&quot; Generate Semua E-Voucher&quot;, type=&quot;primary&quot;):
# Buat ZIP file berisi semua PDF
zip_buffer = io.BytesIO()
with zipfile.ZipFile(zip_buffer, &#x27;w&#x27;, zipfile.ZIP_DEFLATED) as zip_file:
progress_bar = st.progress(0)
status_text = st.empty()
for index, row in df.iterrows():
status_text.text(f&quot;Generating voucher {index + 1}/{len(df)}...&quot;)
pdf_file = create_pdf(row)
zip_file.writestr(
f&quot;Voucher_{row[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;]}.pdf&quot;,
pdf_file.getvalue()
)
progress_bar.progress((index + 1) / len(df))
zip_buffer.seek(0)
status_text.text(&quot;&quot;)
st.success(f&quot; Berhasil generate **{len(df)} voucher**!&quot;)
st.download_button(
label=&quot; Download Semua Voucher (ZIP)&quot;,
data=zip_buffer,
file_name=&quot;all_vouchers.zip&quot;,
mime=&quot;application/zip&quot;,
type=&quot;primary&quot;
)
# Download individual
st.write(&quot;---&quot;)
st.write(&quot;### Download Voucher Individual:&quot;)
# Gunakan selectbox untuk menghindari terlalu banyak button
selected_order = st.selectbox(
&quot;Pilih Order ID:&quot;,
options=df[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;].tolist(),
format_func=lambda x: f&quot;{x} - {df[df[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;]==x][&#x27;Nama_Tamu&#x27;].values[0]}&quot;
)
if selected_order:
selected_row = df[df[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;] == selected_order].iloc[0]
pdf_file = create_pdf(selected_row)
st.download_button(
label=f&quot; Download Voucher - {selected_row[&#x27;Nama_Tamu&#x27;]}&quot;,
data=pdf_file,
file_name=f&quot;Voucher_{selected_row[&#x27;Order_ID&#x27;]}.pdf&quot;,
mime=&quot;application/pdf&quot;,
key=f&quot;single_download_{selected_order}&quot;
)
except Exception as e:
st.error(f&quot; Terjadi kesalahan: {str(e)}&quot;)
st.info(&quot;Pastikan format file Excel sudah benar.&quot;)</code></pre></div></div></pre><hr/><h2> Fitur Tambahan</h2><div class="overflow-x-auto"><table node="[object Object]" utils/ai_validator.py**\n\n```python\nimport pandas as pd\nimport re\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\nclass AIVoucherValidator:\n \"\"\"AI-Powered Data Validation \u0026 Smart Suggestions\"\"\"\n \n def __init__(self):\n self.warnings = []\n self.errors = []\n self.suggestions = []\n \n def validate_dataframe(self, df, required_columns):\n \"\"\"Validasi lengkap dengan AI suggestions\"\"\"\n self._check_columns(df, required_columns)\n self._check_data_types(df)\n self._check_duplicates(df)\n self._check_date_format(df)\n self._check_status_values(df)\n self._smart_suggestions(df)\n \n return {\n 'is_valid': len(self.errors) == 0,\n 'errors': self.errors,\n 'warnings': self.warnings,\n 'suggestions': self.suggestions\n }\n \n def _check_columns(self, df, required_columns):\n missing = [col for col in required_columns if col not in df.columns]\n if missing:\n self.errors.append(f\" Kolom wajib tidak ditemukan: {', '.join(missing)}\")\n \n def _check_data_types(self, df):\n if 'Order_ID' in df.columns:\n if df['Order_ID'].isnull().any():\n self.errors.append(\" Order_ID tidak boleh kosong\")\n \n if 'Nama_Tamu' in df.columns:\n empty_names = df['Nama_Tamu'].isnull().sum()\n if empty_names \u003e 0:\n self.warnings.append(f\" {empty_names} baris tanpa Nama Tamu\")\n \n def _check_duplicates(self, df):\n if 'Order_ID' in df.columns:\n duplicates = df['Order_ID'].duplicated().sum()\n if duplicates \u003e 0:\n self.warnings.append(f\" Ditemukan {duplicates} Order_ID duplikat\")\n \n def _check_date_format(self, df):\n for col in ['Check_in', 'Check_out']:\n if col in df.columns:\n try:\n pd.to_datetime(df[col])\n except:\n self.errors.append(f\" Format tanggal {col} tidak valid\")\n \n def _check_status_values(self, df):\n if 'Status' in df.columns:\n valid_status = ['Lunas', 'Pending', 'DP', 'Cancel']\n invalid = df[~df['Status'].isin(valid_status)]['Status'].unique()\n if len(invalid) \u003e 0:\n self.suggestions.append(f\" Status tidak standar: {list(invalid)}\")\n \n def _smart_suggestions(self, df):\n \"\"\"AI Smart Suggestions\"\"\"\n if len(df) \u003e 100:\n self.suggestions.append(\" Data besar (\u003e100), pertimbangkan batch processing\")\n \n if 'Check_in' in df.columns and 'Check_out' in df.columns:\n try:\n df['Check_in'] = pd.to_datetime(df['Check_in'])\n df['Check_out'] = pd.to_datetime(df['Check_out'])\n df['Duration'] = (df['Check_out'] - df['Check_in']).dt.days\n \n avg_duration = df['Duration'].mean()\n if avg_duration \u003e 30:\n self.suggestions.append(f\" Rata-rata durasi {avg_duration:.0f} hari (panjang)\")\n except:\n pass\n \n def auto_correct(self, df):\n \"\"\"Auto-correct common issues\"\"\"\n df_corrected = df.copy()\n \n # Trim whitespace\n for col in df_corrected.select_dtypes(include=['object']).columns:\n df_corrected[col] = df_corrected[col].astype(str).str.strip()\n \n # Standardize status\n if 'Status' in df_corrected.columns:\n status_map = {\n 'lunas': 'Lunas', 'LUNAS': 'Lunas',\n 'pending': 'Pending', 'PENDING': 'Pending',\n 'dp': 'DP', 'DP': 'DP',\n 'cancel': 'Cancel', 'CANCEL': 'Cancel'\n }\n df_corrected['Status'] = df_corrected['Status'].map(\n lambda x: status_map.get(x, x)\n )\n \n return df_corrected\n```\n\n---\n\n## **4. utils/pdf_generator.py**\n\n```python\nfrom reportlab.pdfgen import canvas\nfrom Config\n\nclass VoucherPDFGenerator:\n def __init__(self, logo_image=None):\n self.logo_image = logo_image\n self.config = Config()\n \n def create_voucher(self, row):\n buffer = io.BytesIO()\n c = canvas.Canvas(buffer, pagesize=A4)\n width, height = A4\n \n # === HEADER WITH LOGO ===\n self._draw_header(c, width, height, row)\n \n # === CONTENT ===\n self._draw_content(c, width, height, row)\n \n # === QR CODE ===\n self._draw_qr(c, width, height, row)\n \n # === FOOTER ===\n self._draw_footer(c, width, height)\n \n c.showPage()\n c.save()\n buffer.seek(0)\n return buffer\n \n def User dapat mengupload file `.xlsx` berisi data voucher.\n - Kolom yang diperlukan:\n - `Order_ID` (ID pesanan)\n - `Nama_Tamu` (Nama pemesan)\n - `Properti` (Nama hotel/properti)\n - `Layanan` (Jenis layanan, e.g., \"Hajj Package\")\n - `Check_in` (Tanggal check-in)\n - `Check_out` (Tanggal check-out)\n - `Status` (Status pembayaran, e.g., \"Paid\", \"Pending\")\n\n2. **Logo Tamima**\n - Tambahkan logo **Tamima Hajj \u0026 Umrah Service** di header voucher.\n - Logo bisa diupload oleh user atau menggunakan logo default (`logo_tamima.png`).\n - Posisi logo: **kiri atas** (ukuran proporsional).\n\n3. **Generate QR Code**\n - Setiap voucher memiliki **QR Code** yang berisi:\n ```\n OrderID:{Order_ID}|Guest:{Nama_Tamu}|Status:{Status}\n ```\n - QR Code ditempatkan di **kanan bawah** voucher.\n\n4. **Download Voucher**\n - Opsi **Single Download**: User bisa memilih voucher mana yang ingin didownload (PDF).\n - Opsi **Bulk Download**: Semua voucher dikompres dalam **file ZIP**.\n - Nama file PDF: `Voucher_{Order_ID}_{Nama_Tamu}.pdf`\n\n5. **Desain Voucher**\n - Ukuran: **A4** (portrait).\n - Header: Judul **\"E-VOUCHER TAMIMA\"** (bold, ukuran 18pt).\n - Detail voucher: Tabel rapi dengan format:\n ```\n Order ID : [Order_ID]\n Nama Tamu : [Nama_Tamu]\n Properti : [Properti]\n Layanan : [Layanan]\n Check-in : [Check_in]\n Check-out : [Check_out]\n Status : [Status]\n ```\n - Footer: Syarat \u0026 ketentuan (font miring, ukuran 9pt).\n - Warna garis pemisah: **emas (#D4AF37)**.\n\n6. **Validasi Data**\n - Jika kolom yang diperlukan tidak ada, tampilkan **error message**.\n - Jika file Excel tidak valid, tampilkan **pesan kesalahan**.\n\n7. **UI/UX**\n - Tampilan **responsive** (bisa diakses di mobile/desktop).\n - Progress bar saat generate banyak voucher.\n - Tombol download berwarna **hijau (#4CAF50)**.\n - Sidebar untuk **upload logo custom**.\n\n8. **Teknologi yang Digunakan**\n - **Streamlit** (untuk web app).\n - **Pandas** (untuk membaca Excel).\n - **QRCode** (untuk generate QR).\n - **ReportLab** (untuk generate PDF).\n - **Pillow** (untuk handling logo).\n\n### ** Contoh Data Excel (Format)**\n| Order_ID | Nama_Tamu | Properti | Layanan | Check_in | Check_out | Status |\n|----------|------------|----------------|--------------|-----------|-----------|--------|\n| INV-001 | Ahmad | Hotel Mekkah | Hajj Package | 2024-06-01| 2024-06-10| Paid |\n| INV-002 | Budi | Hotel Madinah | Umrah Package| 2024-07-15| 2024-07-20| Pending|\n\n### ** Output yang Diharapkan**\n1. **Preview Data**: Tampilkan 5 baris pertama dari Excel.\n2. **Download Button**:\n - Single: ` Download Voucher - [Nama_Tamu]`\n - Bulk: ` Download All Vouchers (ZIP)`\n3. **Contoh Voucher PDF**:\n - Header: Logo Tamima + Judul \"E-VOUCHER TAMIMA\".\n - Body: Detail pesanan + QR Code.\n - Footer: Syarat \u0026 ketentuan.\n\n### ** Struktur Folder**\n```\ntamima-voucher-app/\n app.py # Kode utama Streamlit\n logo_tamima.png # Logo default\n requirements.txt\n```\n\n### ** Contoh `requirements.txt`**\n```\nstreamlit==1.28.0\npandas==2.0.3\nqrcode==7.4.2\nPillow==10.0.0\nreportlab==4.0.4\nopenpyxl==3.1.2\n```\n\n---\n### ** Instruksi Tambahan untuk AI**\n1. **Gunakan `st.set_page_config()`** untuk judul dan icon halaman.\n2. **Validasi file Excel** sebelum diproses.\n3. **Hapus file sementara** (QR Code) setelah PDF generated.\n4. **Optimasi performa** untuk handle banyak data (100+ voucher).\n5. **Berikan feedback visual** (progress bar, notifikasi sukses/gagal).\n\n---\n### ** Output yang Diharapkan dari AI**\nKode **Streamlit** yang siap **copy-paste-run** dengan fitur:\n Upload Excel Preview Data Generate Voucher (PDF + QR + Logo) Download (Single/ZIP).\n\n---\n**Catatan:**\n- Jika logo tidak ditemukan, gunakan **placeholder** atau tampilkan **peringatan**.\n- Pastikan **QR Code bisa discan** dengan aplikasi pembaca QR standar.\n\n---\n**Prompt ini sudah teruji bekerja baik dengan:**\n- **GitHub Copilot** (VS Code)\n- **Blackbox AI**\n- **ChatGPT 4 / Claude 3**"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"28:Tab8,"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"Buat aplikasi web berbasis **Streamlit** bernama **Tamima EVoucher Generator** untuk membuat dan mencetak **PDF voucher** dari file Excel. di-deploy.\n\n### File: `app.py`\n\n```python\nimport streamlit as st\nimport pandas as pd\nimport qrcode\nfrom PIL import Image\nfrom reportlab.pdfgen import canvas\nfrom reportlab.lib.pagesizes import A4\nfrom reportlab.lib.utils import ImageReader\nfrom reportlab.lib import colors\nimport io\nimport os\nimport zipfile\n\n# ====================== KONFIGURASI HALAMAN ======================\nst.set_page_config(\n page_title=\"Tamima E-Voucher Generator\",\n page_icon=\"\",\n layout=\"wide\",\n initial_sidebar_state=\"expanded\"\n)\n\n# ====================== STYLE .stButton\u003ebutton {\n width: 100%;\n border-radius: 5px;\n font-weight: bold;\n }\n \u003c/style\u003e\n \"\"\", unsafe_allow_html=True)\n\n# ====================== FUNGSI UTILITAS ======================\n\ndef load_logo(logo_option, uploaded_logo_file):\n \"\"\"\n Memuat logo berdasarkan pilihan user (Default atau Upload Custom).\n Returns PIL Image object or None.\n \"\"\"\n logo. Pastikan format PNG/JPG.\")\n else:\n st.sidebar.warning(\"Silakan upload file logo.\")\n else:\n # Default Logo\n if os.path.exists(\"logo_tamima.png\"):\n try:\n logo_image = Image.open(\"logo_tamima.png\")\n except Exception:\n st.sidebar.warning(\"File logo_tamima.png ditemukan tapi rusak.\")\n else:\n st.sidebar.warning(\"File 'logo_tamima.png' tidak ditemukan di folder proyek.\")\n return logo_image\n\ndef generate_qr_bytes(data):\n \"\"\"\n Generate QR Code dan return sebagai BytesIO (in-memory).\n \"\"\"\n qr = qrcode.QRCode(\n version=1,\n error_correction=qrcode.constants.ERROR_CORRECT_L,\n box_size=10,\n border=2\n )\n qr.add_data(data)\n qr.make(fit=True)\n img = qr.make_image(fill_color=\"black\", back_color=\"white\")\n \n buffer = io.BytesIO()\n img.save(buffer, format='PNG')\n buffer.seek(0)\n return buffer\n\ndef create_pdf_voucher(row, logo_image):\n \"\"\"\n Membuat PDF voucher untuk satu baris data menggunakan ReportLab.\n \"\"\"\n buffer = io.BytesIO()\n c = canvas.Canvas(buffer, pagesize=A4)\n width, height = A4\n \n # --- HEADER ---\n # Logo\n if logo_image:\n logo_reader = ImageReader(logo_image)\n # Posisi: Kiri Atas (x=50, y=height-100), Ukuran: 100x80\n c.drawImage(logo_reader, x=50, y=height - 100, width=100, height=80, preserveAspectRatio=True)\n \n # Judul\n c.setFont(\"Helvetica-Bold\", 20)\n c.setFillColor(colors.HexColor(\"#1E3A8A\")) # Biru Tua\n c.drawString(160, height - 80, \"E-VOUCHER TAMIMA\")\n \n c.setFont(\"Helvetica\", 12)\n c.setFillColor(colors.black)\n c.drawString(160, height - 100, \"Hajj \u0026 Umrah Service\")\n \n # Garis Pemisah Emas\n c.setStrokeColor(colors.HexColor(\"#D4AF37\"))\n c.setLineWidth(2)\n c.line(50, height - 115, width - 50, height - 115)\n \n # --- BODY (DETAIL DATA) ---\n c.setFont(\"Helvetica-Bold\", 11)\n c.setFillColor(colors.black)\n start_y = height - 150\n line_height = 25\n \n # Mapping label dan data\n fields = [\n (\"Order ID\", str(row['Order_ID'])),\n (\"Nama Tamu\", str(row['Nama_Tamu'])),\n (\"Properti\", str(row['Properti'])),\n (\"Layanan\", str(row['Layanan'])),\n (\"Check-in\", str(row['Check_in'])),\n (\"Check-out\", str(row['Check_out'])),\n (\"Status\", str(row['Status']))\n ]\n \n current_y = start_y\n for label, value in fields:\n c.drawString(60, current_y, f\"{label}:\")\n c.setFont(\"Helvetica\", 11)\n c.drawString(150, current_y, value)\n c.setFont(\"Helvetica-Bold\", 11)\n current_y -= line_height\n \n # --- QR CODE ---\n # Format: OrderID:{Order_ID}|Guest:{Nama_Tamu}|Status:{Status}\n qr_content = f\"OrderID:{row['Order_ID']}|Guest:{row['Nama_Tamu']}|Status:{row['Status']}\"\n qr_buffer = generate_qr_bytes(qr_content)\n qr_reader = ImageReader(qr_buffer)\n \n # Posisi QR: Kanan Tengah\n qr_size = 120\n qr_x = width - 200\n qr_y = height - 250\n c.drawImage(qr_reader, x=qr_x, y=qr_y, width=qr_size, height=qr_size)\n \n c.setFont(\"Helvetica-Oblique\", 9)\n c.drawCentredString(qr_x + (qr_size/2), qr_y - 15, \"Scan untuk verifikasi\")\n \n # --- FOOTER ---\n c.setStrokeColor(colors.lightgrey)\n c.setLineWidth(1)\n c.line(50, 80, width - 50, 80)\n \n c.setFont(\"Helvetica-Oblique\", 9)\n c.setFillColor(colors.darkgrey)\n c.drawString(50, 60, \"Syarat \u0026 Ketentuan:\")\n c.drawString(50, 45, \"1. Voucher berlaku 6 bulan sejak tanggal pembelian.\")\n c.drawString(50, 30, \"2. Tidak dapat digabung dengan promo lainnya.\")\n c.drawString(50, 15, \"3. Tunjukkan voucher ini saat check-in.\")\n \n c.showPage()\n c.save()\n buffer.seek(0)\n return buffer\n\n# ====================== APLIKASI UTAMA ======================\n\ndef main():\n # Judul Utama\n st.markdown('\u003cp class=\"main-header\"\u003e Tamima E-Voucher Generator\u003c/p\u003e', unsafe_allow_html=True)\n st.write(\"Unggah file Excel untuk membuat voucher PDF otomatis dengan Logo \u0026 QR Code.\")\n \n # --- SIDEBAR PENGATURAN ---\n st.sidebar.header(\" Pengaturan\")\n logo_option = st.sidebar.radio(\n \"Pilih Sumber Logo:\",\n [\"Default\", \"Upload Custom\"],\n index=0\n )\n \n uploaded_logo_file = None\n if logo_option == \"Upload Custom\":\n uploaded_logo_file = st.sidebar.file_uploader(\n \"Upload Logo (PNG/JPG)\", \n type=[\"png\", \"jpg\", \"jpeg\"],\n help=\"Ukuran disarankan: 500x500 px, background transparan.\"\n )\n \n logo_image = load_logo(logo_option, uploaded_logo_file)\n if logo_image:\n st.sidebar.success(\"Logo berhasil dimuat.\")\n else:\n st.sidebar.info(\"Voucher akan dibuat tanpa logo.\")\n \n st.sidebar.markdown(\"---\")\n st.sidebar.write(\" 2024 Tamima Hajj \u0026 Umrah\")\n \n # --- MAIN CONTENT ---\n uploaded_file = st.file_uploader(\" Upload File Excel (.xlsx)\", type=[\"xlsx\"])\n \n if uploaded_file is not None:\n try:\n # Baca Excel\n df = pd.read_excel(uploaded_file)\n \n # Validasi Kolom\n required_cols = ['Order_ID', 'Nama_Tamu', 'Properti', 'Layanan', 'Check_in', 'Check_out', 'Status']\n missing_cols = [col for col in required_cols if col not in df.columns]\n \n if missing_cols:\n st.error(f\" **Kolom Tidak Ditemukan:** {', '.join(missing_cols)}\")\n st.info(f\"Pastikan file Excel memiliki kolom berikut: {', '.join(required_cols)}\")\n st.stop()\n \n # Preview Data\n st.success(f\" File berhasil dibaca! Total **{len(df)}** data voucher.\")\n with st.expander(\" Preview Data Excel\"):\n st.dataframe(df, use_container_width=True)\n \n st.markdown(\"---\")\n st.header(\" Opsi Download\")\n \n # Pilihan Mode Download\n download_mode = st.radio(\n \"Pilih metode download:\",\n [\"Download Single Voucher\", \"Download Semua (ZIP)\"],\n horizontal=True\n )\n \n if download_mode == \"Download Single Voucher\":\n # Pilih Order ID\n order_list = df['Order_ID'].astype(str).tolist()\n selected_order = st.selectbox(\n \"Pilih Order ID:\",\n options=order_list,\n index=0\n )\n \n # Ambil data baris terpilih\n selected_row = df[df['Order_ID'].astype(str) == selected_order].iloc[0]\n \n # Generate PDF Preview (Opsional, bisa langsung download)\n if st.button(\" Generate \u0026 Download Voucher Ini\", type=\"primary\", key=\"btn_single\"):\n with st.spinner(\"Sedang membuat PDF...\"):\n try:\n pdf_buffer = create_pdf_voucher(selected_row, logo_image)\n file_name = f\"Voucher_{selected_row['Order_ID']}.pdf\"\n \n st.download_button(\n label=\" Klik untuk Download PDF\",\n data=pdf_buffer,\n file_name=file_name,\n mime=\"application/pdf\",\n key=\"download_single_pdf\"\n )\n st.success(\"PDF siap diunduh!\")\n except Exception as e:\n st.error(f\"Gagal membuat PDF: {str(e)}\")\n \n else: # Download Semua (ZIP)\n st.warning(f\" Anda akan membuat **{len(df)}** file PDF dalam satu ZIP. Proses mungkin memakan waktu.\")\n \n if st.button(\" Generate \u0026 Download ZIP\", type=\"primary\", key=\"btn_zip\"):\n zip_buffer = io.BytesIO()\n progress_bar = st.progress(0)\n status_text = st.empty()\n \n try:\n with zipfile.ZipFile(zip_buffer, 'w', zipfile.ZIP_DEFLATED) as zip_file:\n for idx, row in df.iterrows():\n # Update Progress\n progress = (idx + 1) / len(df)\n progress_bar.progress(progress)\n status_text.text(f\"Memproses: {row['Nama_Tamu']} ({idx + 1}/{len(df)})\")\n \n # Generate PDF\n pdf_buffer = create_pdf_voucher(row, logo_image)\n \n # Nama file dalam ZIP\n # Sanitasi nama file untuk keamanan\n safe_name = str(row['Nama_Tamu']).replace('/', '_').replace('\\\\', '_')\n zip_filename = f\"Voucher_{row['Order_ID']}_{safe_name}.pdf\"\n \n # Masukkan ke ZIP\n zip_file.writestr(zip_filename, pdf_buffer.getvalue())\n \n zip_buffer.seek(0)\n status_text.success(\" Semua voucher berhasil dibuat!\")\n progress_bar.empty()\n \n st.download_button(\n label=\" Download File ZIP\",\n data=zip_buffer,\n file_name=\"Tamima_Vouchers.zip\",\n mime=\"application/zip\",\n key=\"download_zip_file\"\n )\n \n except Exception as e:\n (\"Check-out\", str(row['Check_out'])),\n (\"Status\", str(row['Status']))\n ]\n \n for i, (label, value) in enumerate(details):\n y_pos = start_y - (i * line_height)\n # Label bold\n c.setFont(\"Helvetica-Bold\", 11)\n c.drawString(label_x, y_pos, f\"{label} :\")\n # Value normal\n c.setFont(\"Helvetica\", 11)\n c.drawString(value_x, y_pos, value)\n \n # === QR CODE ===\n qr_content = f\"OrderID:{row['Order_ID']}|Guest:{row['Nama_Tamu']}|Status:{row['Status']}\"\n qr_buffer = generate_qr_bytes(qr_content)\n \n # ReportLab butuh path file untuk drawImage, jadi buat temp
